软件包 mobios.util

接口摘要
DataLoader This is a general interface that can be used for loading data from files into programs.
ObjectIOManager This is an interface for object input/output management.
 

类摘要

Histogram.BinInfo  
LargeDenseDoubleMatrix2D Large Dense 2-d matrix holding double elements.
MckoiObjectIOManager An implementation of ObjectIOManager based on the Mckoi(http://www.mckoi.com/database) I/O mechanism.
MiscellaneousTool  
Pair This is a simple wrapper to wrap two object together.
